
Chromium Extension to display lyrics for the current song in Google Music from lyricwiki.org

Version 1.0.10:
* Adapted to changes in Google Play (TM) (thanks to dibrial).

Version 1.0.9:
* Lyrics can be selected for copying.
* Adapted to changes in Google Play (TM).

Version 1.0.8:
* Adapted to changes in Google Play (TM).
* Aesthetic adjustments.

Version 1.0.7:
* Adapted to changes in Google Play (TM).

Version 1.0.6:
* Support for more foreign languages added.

Version 1.0.5:
* Works in Google Play (TM).

Version 1.0.4:
* Lyria button removed.
* Small aesthetic changes.

Version 1.0.3:
* Works in https site.

Version 1.0.2:
* Adapted to changes in the web page.

Version 1.0.1:
* Fixed bug that caused the lyrics of the current and previous songs to keep switching.

Version 1.0.0:
* Initial release

This extension uses REST api from lyrics.wikia.com and jquery
